on carbon.\n\nThis is nucleophilic addition of a nitrogen nucleophile to a carbocation electrophile.\n\nMechanistic class: nucleophilic_addition\n\nReaction center: Bond formation between N(:10) and C(:20), with charge neutralization (NH- + CH+ → NH-CH).\n\nSince the task asks for mechanistic classification and the expected output schema is \"mechanistic_label\", I should provide the mechanistic class label.\n\nThe answer should be: nucleophilic_addition"
